---
title: Admin Operations — Sequence Diagram
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Admin
    participant UI as Frontend
    participant API as Backend
    participant MS as Merkle Service
    participant SC as Smart Contract
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    A->>UI: Set deadlines, manage phases
    UI->>SC: startRegistration(regEnd)
    UI->>SC: startVoting(voteEnd)
    UI->>SC: endElection()
    SC-->>UI: PhaseChanged events

    A->>UI: Select & verify pending students
    UI->>API: POST /api/voters/verify-bulk
    API->>DB: UPDATE eligible_to_vote=true
    API->>MS: generateMerkleRoot(wallets)
    API->>MS: generateIdentityMerkleRoot(identities)
    MS-->>API: New roots
    API->>SC: setMerkleRoot + setIdentityMerkleRoot
    SC-->>API: MerkleRootUpdated events

    A->>UI: Upload spreadsheet for codes
    UI->>API: POST /api/admin/generate-codes
    API->>DB: INSERT registration_codes
    API->>MS: generateRegCodeMerkleRoot()
    API->>SC: setRegCodeMerkleRoot(root)
    API->>API: Send batch emails
